Global Petroleum corp said today itlowered the posted cargo prices for number six fuel in the newyork harbor 45 to 75 cts a barrel, effective today.    The decrease brings the prices for one pct sulphur to 20.75dlrs, down 45 cts, two pct sulphur 20.10 dlrs, down 75 cts, 2.2pct sulphur 19.75 dlrs, down 75 cts and 2.5 pct sulphur 19.50dlrs, down 75 cts.    Prices for 0.3 pct and 0.5 pct sulphur remained unchangedat 22.50 and 21.85 dlrs, it said. Reuter&#3;